snippet.title: Amber Heard Says No One Would Believe Johnny Depp In New Audio
snippet.description:
The worst part about this abhorrent view is not that she said it while abusing him, it's the fact that she, i and everyone knows she's right. Unfortunately that's the world we live in when the abuser can claim to be the victim and the victim is dragged through the dirt because of their gender.
